131
00:14:02,284 --> 00:14:05,921
Even you scolded her for
talking like boys.

132
00:14:05,922 --> 00:14:08,990
And if I smoked one cigarette,
what great sin have I committed?

133
00:14:08,991 --> 00:14:14,224
