134
00:14:26,308 --> 00:14:32,673
"It overflowed... the water from
the pitcher overflowed".

135
00:14:34,083 --> 00:14:40,050
"It overflowed for the
eye couldn't hold".

136
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:59,841
